FROM python:3.9-alpine3.12

LABEL maintainer="Rhino Assessment Team <pacu@rhinosecuritylabs.com>"
LABEL pacu.version="1.0.1"

    aws-cli \
    zip

# Install Pacu

COPY ./ ./
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir .

RUN echo 'AWS_EC2_METADATA_DISABLED=true' >> /etc/profile

ENTRYPOINT ["pacu"]
